## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8876e-103">La forma estesa di un nome distinto include una rappresentazione di stringa della proprietà objectGUID di un oggetto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8876e-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8876e-104">Per gli oggetti entità di sicurezza, ad esempio utenti, gruppi e computer, la forma estesa include anche una rappresentazione di stringa della proprietà objectSID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8876e-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8876e-105">Per ulteriori informazioni sulle proprietà objectGUID e objectSID, vedere gli argomenti [Object-Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) e [Object-Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in MSDN all'indirizzo [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8876e-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see the topics [Object-Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) and [Object-Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="8876e-106">Nell'esempio c# seguente viene illustrato come restituire una raccolta di nomi distinti in formato esadecimale.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8876e-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  

```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  

```
